{
  "stem": "7094.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they went for a day outing to look at it, how it was happening.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't know anything about what was going on in the world outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I then said, well, I'll go back to Jaworow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I still thought Jaworow was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then again, fate-- how it can-- By the time the German finished with the Jews, they started taking local population for forced labor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this village had to produce 60 girls to go to work in Germany.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And one of the daughters of the household had to go to Germany, which was a major tragedy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Berlin was very bombarded.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Germany was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I said, well, I'll volunteer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll go instead of you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which they agreed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we had to go to Lublin, to the arbeitsamt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was another sort of conducive situation, because the arbeitsamt had a demand from Berlin, from a [GERMAN], for a domestic.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the girl who was going to go there was bribing him not to go to Berlin, because at that time Berlin was very bombarded.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[CREW COUGHS] So this man at the desk said, fine-- this will solve his problem.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It solved the problem that the daughter could stay with the family.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The man in the arbeitsamt could send off somebody to Berlin instead of the girl who was feeding him with bribing him not to go.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was I, finding myself with all the documents to go to Germany, to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had an address-- Wallen-- Wallenbergstrasse 73-- and Diplom-Ingenieur Lang, who had a demand for the domestic to go there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--this was a--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--salvation, in a way.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because in Germany, they were very accurate and very ex-- very-- very pedantic.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
